# Pre-loaded raw source snapshots (~25MB; regenerate with scripts/fetch_sources.py).
# Provenance records (manifests, findings) stay tracked so checksums and record
# counts survive in git without the payload.
brainstorm/municipal/02-safeheat/data/raw/downloaded/**
!brainstorm/municipal/02-safeheat/data/raw/downloaded/
!brainstorm/municipal/02-safeheat/data/raw/downloaded/*/
!brainstorm/municipal/02-safeheat/data/raw/downloaded/PRELOAD_FINDINGS.md
!brainstorm/municipal/02-safeheat/data/raw/downloaded/*/download_manifest.json
# Derived statistics quoted in the demo must keep their provenance in git (small JSON).
!brainstorm/municipal/02-safeheat/data/raw/downloaded/*/austin_heat_event_climatology.json
